---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Why Clarity. Works"
  description="What makes us different to consultancies and contractors"
  type="WebPage"
  canonicalURL="https://getclarity.win/why-clarity-works"
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Why Clarity. Works</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      A frictionless support model that compounds value over time.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section
    class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-10"
  >
    <p class="text-center">
      You don't need another consultancy. <br />
      <strong>You need momentum.</strong>
    </p>

    <p class="text-center">
      You're already under pressure to make decisions, fast. But clarity is hard
      to find when:
    </p>
    <section class="max-w-lg mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-8 text-left mb-24">
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-left space-y-2">
          <li>Priorities shift weekly</li>
          <li>Stakeholders pull in different directions</li>
          <li>Roadmaps balloon before they're grounded</li>
          <li>Every “solution” seems to need a six-figure SoW</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <p class="text-center">
        You're not short of ideas. You're short of
        <strong>alignment, traction, and certainty</strong>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section
      class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-gray-900 text-white dark:bg-black/50 rounded-lg px-8 py-12 mb-24 text-center space-y-6"
    >
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Clarity. is a Support Plan.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg">
        <em>Not a proposal. Not a contractor. Not a guessing game.</em>
      </p>
      <p>
        You don't need to justify a project. <br />
        You don't need to hire full-time.
      </p>
      <p>
        You need strategic thinking. <strong>On tap</strong>, on cadence, and
        built to fit your world. <br />
        Clarity. delivers that. Quickly. Predictably. Repeatedly.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="italic text-lg text-blue-200">
        “Confident decisions. Made faster, with less risk, and more momentum.”
      </blockquote>
    </section>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">How we work.</h2>
    <section
      class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left mb-24"
    >
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Strategic Rhythm</h3>
        <p>
          <li>You're not booking hours. You're building continuous support.</li>
          <li>We show up consistently.</li>
          <li>No scope creep, no context lost.</li>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Embedded Context</h3>
        <p>
          <li>We integrate quickly, use your language.</li>
          <li>We Work with your team.</li>
          <li>No outside observers. No resets.</li>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Tangible Outcomes</h3>
        <p>Each cycle delivers:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Clarity Sessions</strong> to unblock thinking.</li>
          <li><strong>Clarity Briefs</strong> that summarise decisions.</li>
          <li><strong>Clarity Radar</strong> to catch what's coming next.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">
          Predictable Cost. Zero Overhead.
        </h3>
        <p>
          <li>You choose your Support Plan.</li>
          <li>You pay a fixed amount.</li>
          <li>No surprises.</li>
          <li>No upsells.</li>
          <li>No delays.</li>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Our promise.</h2>
    <section
      class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left"
    >
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-4">You Will Get</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Strategic clarity every cycle.</li>
          <li>A partner who understands your pressure.</li>
          <li>Decisions you can stand behind.</li>
          <li>Momentum that compounds.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-4">You Won't Get</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Hourly billing.</li>
          <li>Decks no one reads.</li>
          <li>Consultants who disappear after a workshop.</li>
          <li>Waiting weeks for someone to “get it”.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation Arrows -->
    <section class="my-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Want to see what you get with Clarity.?
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-12 justify-center items-center">
        <!-- Left Arrow Link -->
        <a
          href="/"
          aria-label="Previous page"
          class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            width="64"
            height="64"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>

        <!-- Right Arrow Link -->
        <a
          href="/what-you-get"
          aria-label="Next page"
          class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            width="64"
            height="64"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center mb-24">
      <p class="text-lg mb-4">Ready?</p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-block bg-black text-white dark:bg-white dark:text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:opacity-90 transition"
      >
        Join the Waitlist
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
